title: Marvel Lucha Libre Edition: El origen de la máscara
overview: The front and back of the "masks" of a tournament that pits Los Técnicos and Los Rudos against each other, two groups of fighters inspired by Super Heroes and Marvel's most iconic villains. Record each instance of the league from the personal perspective of the fighters, culminating in the big event that will award one of them with the coveted belt, crowning him as the new champion.
